songs.title: 3 Times*
songs.lyrics:
Snippet

Looking odee from my side
I said she ain't an eater, oh, she lied, oh, she lied, lied
Woke up to three bitches in my bed
Made me say it three times, "Know you fine, know you fine, fine"
I ain't rocking with no ho niggas or bozo, that's a no-no, nigga, nah, nah
I know they know my fly
